channel.title: [PI] [508] Need a coder to help with my server [PI] [508]
channel.description:
Hey moparscape, i am looking for a PI 508 coder who is willing to help me in making my server, I want to try and make a really good server that people will love and enjoy, im not asking for money from it or nor am i willing to pay for anything since i cannot afford much :P
P.S sorry if this is not the right section for posting for a coder but i dont know were i should post it? SUGGESTION: this forum needs a recruitment section :)
All coders who are willing to help please get back to me Skype: gunnarr5 msn: matt_home_66@hotmail.com (also can email me at this address) Or simply PM me on here :D
